WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:04.000
There are a number of programs organized by student life that offer experiences to connect students to the local culture

00:04.000 --> 00:10.000
These range from over-night trips to the Northern Emirates to conversations with Emirati professionals, mixers with students from other local universities, Ramadan and UAE Etiquette programming and so much more

00:10.000 --> 00:17.000
All NYUAD students are encouraged to be curious about local culture and Campus Life as well as fellow Emirati students are passionate about enabling students to get to know their host country as much as possible

